<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>ARMURERIE BLANCHE | JUDOGI STORE</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syncopate:wght@700&family=Rajdhani:wght@500;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --pure-white: #ffffff;
            --silver: #c0c0c0;
            --gold: #d4af37;
            --dark-card: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.95);
            --accent-silver: #8e8e8e;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a1a 0%, #050505 100%);
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* --- BARRE DE NAVIGATION --- */
        .top-nav {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-group { display: flex; gap: 20px; }

        .btn-nav {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #666;
            font-family: 'Syncopate', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.7em;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-nav:hover { color: var(--pure-white); text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

        /* --- HEADER --- */
        header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Syncopate', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #888, #fff, #888);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* --- GRID DES PRODUITS --- */
        .armory-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            position: relative;
            transition: 0.4s;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--pure-white);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .product-tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px; right: 20px;
            background: var(--pure-white);
            color: #000;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.7em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .product-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .product-img img { max-width: 80%; max-height: 80%; object-fit: contain; }

        .grammage { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9em; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
        h2 { font-family: 'Syncopate'; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #fff; }
        
        .specs { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .specs li { font-size: 0.9em; color: #bbb; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .specs i { color: var(--silver); font-size: 0.7em; }

        .footer-card {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .price { font-size: 1.6em; font-weight: 700; }
        .btn-buy {
            background: var(--pure-white);
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-buy:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.5); transform: scale(1.05); }

        /* --- BONUS --- */
        .bonus-box {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .bonus-card {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .bonus-card i { font-size: 2em; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .bonus-card h4 { color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9em; }
        .bonus-card p { font-size: 0.85em; color: #999; }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="top-nav">
        <div class="nav-group">
            <a href="index.html" class="btn-nav"><i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> Accueil</a>
            <a href="hautdekimono.html" class="btn-nav"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left"></i> Tous les Hauts</a>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-nav" style="cursor: default; opacity: 0.5;">Catégorie : Blanche</div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <h1>Vestes Blanches</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--silver); letter-spacing: 2px;">LA TRADITION RENCONTRE LA PERFORMANCE</p>
    </header>

    <div class="armory-grid">
        
        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-tag">Initiation</div>
            <div class="product-img">
                <img src="IMAGE_BLANC_1.png" alt="Kimono Blanc Léger">
            </div>
            <span class="grammage">450 G/M² - SOUPLLESSE TOTALE</span>
            <h2>ZEN-WHITE LIGHT</h2>
            <ul class="specs">
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Idéal débutants & Randori souple</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> 100% coton respirant</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Liberté de mouvement accrue</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="footer-card">
                <div class="price">69€</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-buy">ARMER</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card" style="border-color: var(--gold);">
            <div class="product-tag" style="background: var(--gold);">Classique</div>
            <div class="product-img">
                <img src="IMAGE_BLANC_2.png" alt="Kimono Blanc Entraînement">
            </div>
            <span class="grammage">650 G/M² - POLYVALENCE</span>
            <h2>BUSHIDO CLASSIC</h2>
            <ul class="specs">
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Le standard du Dojo</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Col renforcé mi-dur</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Rapport qualité/prix imbattable</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="footer-card">
                <div class="price">89€</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-buy" style="background: var(--gold);">ARMER</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-tag">Maître</div>
            <div class="product-img">
                <img src="IMAGE_BLANC_3.png" alt="Kimono Blanc Lourd">
            </div>
            <span class="grammage">850 G/M² - ARMURE TRADITIONNELLE</span>
            <h2>SENSEI MASTER-WHITE</h2>
            <ul class="specs">
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Tissage grain de riz premium</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Coupe japonaise authentique</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Résistance extrême à la traction</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="footer-card">
                <div class="price">135€</div>
                <a href="#" class="btn-buy">ARMER</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="bonus-box">
        <div class="bonus-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-snowflake"></i>
            <h4>Blancheur Éclatante</h4>
            <p>Traitement spécial anti-jaunissement pour garder un blanc pur.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bonus-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-scissors"></i>
            <h4>Coupe Ajustable</h4>
            <p>Design ergonomique qui s'adapte à toutes les carrures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bonus-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-fist"></i>
            <h4>Grip Inégalable</h4>
            <p>Matière texturée pour un contrôle parfait de vos saisies.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>